headline: Northrop Grumman (NOC) Signs a MOU With Ministry of Defence and Ministry of Finance of The Republic of Lithuania
summary: Northrop Grumman Corporation (NYSE:NOC) is one of the 13 Best Aerospace and Defense Stocks to Invest in Now.
